The exotic Mövenpick Hotel Ibn Battuta Gate Dubai is a Moroccan themed, 5-star hotel with 396 rooms. We are looking for a Bellman to join our team.
The ideal candidates must have related job experience in the Hotel industry. He will be welcoming and assisting the guests, facilitating requests and ensuring that tasks are done according to the set standards.
